prompts.frontCover:
A watercolor painting of a funny beach scene. In the center, an elderly East Asian woman, Lao Lao, sits majestically on a throne made of intricately detailed mahjong tiles. She wears a crown, a huge smile, and holds a comically oversized bubble tea with large boba pearls. To her left, kneeling in the sand and looking up at her adoringly, is a cartoon version of Jordan, a young man in his early 20s with short black hair, a bright smile with white teeth, wearing a white t-shirt. To her right, also kneeling and looking up with a happy expression, is a cartoon version of a young woman in her early 20s with long, straight black hair, wearing thin gold-rimmed circular glasses and a yellow top with a red floral pattern. The background is a sunny beach with gentle blue ocean waves and a clear sky. In the center of the image, written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text "Happy Birthday Lao Lao!". The entire image has the soft, flowing colors, artistic brush strokes, and organic paint bleeds characteristic of a watercolor painting on textured paper. Flat 2D artwork.

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
